@startuml
title Policy Expression Language — Grammar Diagram

class "Expression" as Expression
class "LogicalOr" as LogicalOr
class "LogicalAnd" as LogicalAnd
class "Comparison" as Comparison
class "Arithmetic" as Arithmetic
class "Term" as Term
class "Factor" as Factor
class "Primary" as Primary

Expression --> LogicalOr
LogicalOr --> LogicalAnd
LogicalAnd --> Comparison
Comparison --> Arithmetic
Arithmetic --> Term
Term --> Factor
Factor --> Primary

note right of LogicalOr
  Logical operators (lowest precedence):
  ||, &&
end note

note right of Comparison
  Comparison operators:
  == != < <= > >=
end note

note right of Arithmetic
  Additive:
  + -
end note

note right of Term
  Multiplicative (highest among operators):
  * /
end note

note bottom of Primary
  Primary tokens:
  - Number literals
  - Identifiers (e.g. score.PNRS, OSS.total)
  - Parenthesized expressions

  Implemented in:
  src/api/policyParser/tokens.ts
  src/api/policyParser/parser.ts
end note

@enduml
